WEBVTT

00:05:59.148 --> 00:06:02.034
or religious, through
the coexistent presence --

00:06:02.058 --> 00:06:05.770
were all lost in the misguided
and visionless modernization

00:06:05.794 --> 00:06:07.158
of the built environment.

00:06:07.782 --> 00:06:09.047
Allow me an aside.

00:06:09.467 --> 00:06:13.650
When I read about heterogeneous urbanism
in other parts of the world,

00:06:13.674 --> 00:06:16.146
involving ethnic neighborhoods
in British cities

00:06:16.170 --> 00:06:18.279
or around Paris or Brussels,

00:06:18.303 --> 00:06:21.897
I recognize the beginning
of the kind of instability

00:06:21.921 --> 00:06:24.851
we have witnessed
so disastrously here in Syria.

00:06:26.027 --> 00:06:28.233
We have severely destroyed cities,

00:06:28.257 --> 00:06:31.438
such as Homs, Aleppo,
Daraa and many others,